{"tid":2045274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果美國取消香港關系法都打擊唔到支那，抗爭者係咪已經算輸撚左？","createTime":"2020-05-31T16:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T03:15:04.000Z","uid":229095,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"66933dd81059bf16725e06bfbf6a3ec6f5fa7f2d","tid":2045274,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"搞左成年咩都爭取唔到<br />\n而家支那終於推你一把<br />\n如果都係搞唔掂<br />\n如果支那真係有plan b<br />\n咁我地係咪已經冇棋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩我都應該可以全身而退<br />\n抗爭左咁耐真係好撚厭<br />\n由期而家班兒登仔講d野唔啱聽就話人五毛<br />\n比你贏左，過二三十年你咪又係建制唔聽人意見個d人囉<br />\n有咩分別姐<br />\n成日搞埋d送頭行動<br />\n我覺得你班撚樣只係在乎過過程而唔係結果囉<br />\n出埋晒d fake new標題post都可以上熱門<br />\n然後下面班弱智可以信到十足十<br />\n你班黃屍一撚樣都係冇腦咋<br />\n<br />\n唔洗cap我出過咩post啦兒登垃圾<br />\n我自己cap, 我係五毛我係分化撚失敗撚<br />\n屌晒你地班垃圾老母<br />\n肯撚定光復唔到香港啊<br />\n而家我聽到光復香港都打晒冷震<br />\n呢隻game你自己玩埋佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nrZfRJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nrZfRJ.jpg&h=79b1f0b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32f041d833480eeb5815133bb82998b802c15e7a","tid":2045274,"uid":229095,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T16:52:56.000Z","msg":"五毛開po冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa054599b20e8929d16dc0baf1a6d7d08a94bd18","tid":2045274,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T16:53:27.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e7230da669e7eca05928cefe7a53d19fd2c371","tid":2045274,"uid":66817,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"等睇連登仔話五毛分化撚失敗撚block拉"},{"pid":"db8b1cfdd5768555658b36ad15a8b6416d245d98","tid":2045274,"uid":58209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T16:59:51.000Z","m